     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       gttng t mnml: ll th nf y nd t trck
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       <img alt="" src="http://mnmlist.com/fotos/20090907moleskine.jpg"/>
       <small>
        Pht crtsy f
        <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/alt1040/11220515//">
         lt1040
        </a>
        .
       </small>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://mnmlist.com/about/#leo">
        By L
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       Th blg ‘ mlln mnkys typng’ (pprntly dfnct) hs n ntrstng ldr pst clld
       <a href="http://www.douglasjohnston.net/weblog/archives/2005/06/27/beginners-mind/">
        Bgnnr’s Mnd
       </a>
       n whch th thr mks  lst f ll th nfrmtn h nds t trck.
      </p>
      Dgls tks  “bgnnr’s mnd” pprch nd mks  lst f vry typ f nfrmtn h nds t kp trck f, ncldng bt nt lmtd t:
      <br/>
      <ul>
       <li>
        tsks
       </li>
       <li>
        dlgtd tsks t fllw p n
       </li>
       <li>
        spndng
       </li>
       <li>
        ppntmnts
       </li>
       <li>
        prjcts
       </li>
       <li>
        cntct nf
       </li>
       <li>
        ddlns
       </li>
       <li>
        dly nws
       </li>
       <li>
        lgns/psswrds
       </li>
       <li>
        cr ln nf
       </li>
       <li>
        rrnds
       </li>
      </ul>
      Tht’s nt th ntr lst, bt h ws bl t whttl t dwn t bt  dzn thngs t trck. And I thnk tht’s lss thn mst ppl, bcs h gt t dwn t th ssntls (fr hm). Rlz, f crs, tht vryn’s nds r dffrnt, nd wht’s ssntl fr n prsn sn’t ssntl fr nthr.

Stll, t’s  sfl xrcs. Mk  lst f vrythng y nd t trck, nd thn fgr t th smplst, mst nttv wy t trck thm. Usng th smplst tls.
      <br/>
      <span id="more-103">
      </span>
      <br/>
      As n xrcs, hr’s my lst:
      <br/>
      <ul>
       <li>
        tsks
       </li>
       <li>
        ppntmnts
       </li>
       <li>
        cntcts
       </li>
       <li>
        lgns/psswrds
       </li>
       <li>
        hlth/ftnss lgs (tng cln, xrcsng)
       </li>
      </ul>
      It’s pssbl I’m mssng  cpl thngs. And ths sn’t th mst mnml lst pssbl. Bt lt m tll y hw I’v gttn t dwn ths fr, nd thn w’ll lk t hw I cld gt t t b vn mr mnml.
      <p>
       <strong>
        Hw I Whttld It Dwn
       </strong>
       <br/>
       A cpl f yrs g, my lst wld hv bn mch lngr. Fr xmpl, t n tm I trckd ll my spndng, ll my dbt, vry bll nd whn t ws d. I dn’t nymr. At n pnt I trckd ll my tng, vry clr, nd vry clr I brnd thrgh xrcs. I ls hd  mch mr cmplctd prdctvty systm (bsd n
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net/2007/02/beginners-guide-to-gtd/">
        <span class="caps">
         GTD
        </span>
       </a>
       ), whr I trckd nt nly tsks (“nxt ctns”) bt prjcts nd smdy/myb tms nd dlgtd tsks nd s n. At n pnt I hd  lst f gls nd sb-gls nd ctn tms fr ch n. And mr, bt I wn’t br y wth ll th dtls.
      </p>
      Slwly, I’v whttld dwn my nds:
      <br/>
      <ol>
       <li>
        I’v slwly chngd my wrk t st my nds. Ths hs tkn  cpl f yrs, bt t’s bn  cnscs ffrt t wrk fr myslf, n my wn trms, nd smplfy wht I d.
       </li>
       <li>
        As  rslt, I hv fwr nds — I dn’t nd s mny ppntmnts, mtngs, prjcts, nd s n.
       </li>
       <li>
        I slwly gt t f dbt nd thn fcsd n svng, llwng m t wrry lss bt fnncs. Nw I py sm blls n dvnc, t-py thrs, nd kp  smll srpls n my chckng ccnt s I dn’t nd t wrry bt t-py nd ncdntl lvng xpnss.
       </li>
       <li>
        I’v rdcd my cmmnctn nds rcntly.
       </li>
       <li>
        I’v stppd mkng s mny ppntmnts nd hvng s mny mtngs.
       </li>
       <li>
        I’v stppd wrryng bt gls. Whch mns I dn’t nd t trck thm r thr ctn stps.
       </li>
       <li>
        I’v gttn my tng nd xrcsng hbts t  pnt whr I dn’t nd t b s bsssv. I’v dvlpd  rlxd tttd twrds hlth, by njyng my xrcs nd hlthy fds. I nw trck thngs thrgh
        <a href="http://daytum.com/leobabauta">
         my dytm
        </a>
        , jst fr fn, nd s  mtvtr.
       </li>
       <li>
        I’v ls gvn p n rdng nws r wrryng bt kpng p wth blgs. I lv rdng blgs (nt nws) bt I dn’t fl th nd t kp p wth thm. I jst rd fr plsr, wth n prssr.
       </li>
      </ol>
      I’ll wrt bt mny f ths thngs n ltr psts, s thy dsrv sm fcs f thr wn. Th pnt s, ths s pssbl, nd y cn rthnk yr nds s wll, nd chng thm vr tm.
      <p>
       It’s ls mprtnt t nt tht mst f ths chngs hvn’t cm bcs f my lfstyl, bt my tttd: I wrry lss bt gls, trckng clrs, fnncs, nd th lk, nd bcs I wrry lss, I trck vrythng lss.
      </p>
      <strong>
       Hw I Cn Pr It Dwn Frthr
      </strong>
      <br/>
      Bt I’m nt s mnml s pssbl. Hr’s wht I cn d, nd wll prbbly d, n th cmng mnths, n rdr t rdc my nd t trck nfrmtn:
      <br/>
      <ol>
       <li>
        Adpt n n-th-mmnt tsk pprch. I’ll wrt bt ths sn. Bsclly, t mns I dn’t kp trck f gls, prjcts r vn tsks. Jst sk myslf ch mrnng: “Wht d I wnt t ccmplsh tdy?” Thn ch mmnt, wrk n wht I’m mst pssnt bt.
       </li>
       <li>
        Drp ppntmnts lmst ntrly. Tll ppl t cll/ml m n th dy, nd w st  tm. If I kp my dys wd pn, sttng  tm shldn’t b hrd. I mstly wrk lk ths lrdy.
       </li>
       <li>
        Lt tch trck my cntcts nd psswrds fr m. I lrdy mstly d ths wth Gml — t tmtclly strs ml ddrsss nd I n lngr wrry bt thm. My phn mstly strs my phn cntcts. I dn’t s  psswrd mngr bt mght d tht. Whl ths dsn’t mn I wll n lngr nd t str ths nf, t wll mn I n lngr nd t wrry bt t.
       </li>
       <li>
        I dn’t nd t trck xrcs nd cln tng t ths pnt. Bt I fl bttr dng t, fr nw. Myb n  cpl mnths I’ll b n  plc whr t’s nncssry.
       </li>
      </ol>
      Of crs, nn f ths sltns wll wrk fr vryn. I lst thm hr t shw hw t’s pssbl t chng yr tttd nd yr nds s kpng trck f nf bcms prtty mnml.
      <p>
       <small>
       </small>
      </p>
